<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us - AgriFusion</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flowbite/2.2.1/flowbite.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-green-100 min-h-screen flex flex-col">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div>
    <%- include('header') %>
  </div>

  <!-- About Us Section -->
  <section class="flex-1 px-4 py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-6">About AgriFusion 🌱</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        At AgriFusion, we’re building a future where farmers are empowered and consumers receive the best. 
        Our mission is simple: <span class="font-semibold text-green-700">eliminate middlemen</span>, ensure <span class="font-semibold text-green-700">fair pricing</span> for farmers, and deliver <span class="font-semibold text-green-700">high-quality produce</span> directly to your doorstep.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-10 text-left">
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">🌾 Empowering Farmers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We provide farmers a transparent platform to list and sell their products without the interference of intermediaries.
            This helps them get the value they truly deserve.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">🛒 Connecting Consumers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our marketplace allows consumers to buy directly from farmers, ensuring fresh produce, traceability, and support to the real heroes of agriculture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">📈 Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            To revolutionize the agriculture ecosystem by using technology to support sustainable farming and ethical trade practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">🤝 Community First</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            AgriFusion is more than a marketplace — it's a community that values trust, transparency, and growth for everyone involved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="mt-8">
    <%- include('footer') %>
  </div>

  <!-- Flowbite JS -->
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flowbite/2.2.1/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
